        <p><%= t('projects_aws_desc', 'Designed and implemented a secure Virtual Private Cloud (VPC) on AWS with public/private subnets, Security Groups acting as stateful firewalls, and Network ACLs for stateless traffic filtering. Configured secure routing and internet access via NAT Gateway.') %></p>
