        <p><%= t('projects_siem_desc', 'Designed and implemented a Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) system for centralized logging and security analysis. Integrated various data sources to detect security incidents and automate response measures.') %></p>
        <div class="tech-used">
          <span>SIEM</span>
          <span>Security Analysis</span>
          <span>Log Management</span>
